  - Keyworded ~arm per request. Builds native but fails at cross-compiles.

  05 May 2008; Stefaan De Roeck <stefaan@gentoo.org> autofs-5.0.3-r5.ebuild:
  Patch patches in temporary directory (fixes bug #220315)

