*autofs-3.1.7-r5 (17 Nov 2002)
  
  17 Nov 2002; Brad Cowan <bcowan@gebtoo.org> autofs-3.1.7-r5.ebuild,
  files/digest-autofs-3.1.7-r5, files/ldap_config.patch, files/autofs.rc8 :

